QFITS Reference Manual Modules

Here is a list of all modules:
  • FITS caching capabilities
  • Get various names (filenames, dir names,...)
  • FITS header handling
  • Pixel loader for FITS images.
  • FITS data block MD5 computation routine
  • FITS header reading/writing
  • FITS table handling
  • Get date/time, possibly in ISO8601 format
  • Simple FITS access routines
  • POSIX-compatible extended memory handling
